{
  "texts": [
    "First, the following keywords were used: wind, energy, DFIG, SSR, SSCI, SSTI, control, and systems; search results amounted to 3646 papers with the range from 2001 to 2024.",
    "Subsequently, 450 papers were eliminated based on the criterion like DFIG-based WECS, language, and peer-reviewed journals.",
    "This helped to filter sources to only those in English language and with high quality publications.",
    "An author-based analysis was also made which deals with the most productive and influential authors in the area using means such as citation and h-index.",
    "Networking of co-authors was also examined to determine collaboration patterns that provided further information on who was most active in the field."
  ]
}